==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Daphne
<hw>Daph"ne</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., a laurel tree,
from Gr. <grk>da`fnh</grk>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A
genus of diminutive Shrubs, mostly evergreen, and with fragrant
blossoms.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Myth.)</fld> <def>A nymph of Diana, fabled to have
been changed into a laurel tree.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Daphnetin</ent>⟦br⟧
